  .services
    .title Save Time & Maximize Revenue
    .subtitle We handle all the dirty work so you can more time for [ x ]
    ul
      li
        =image_tag 'icon_cleaning.png'
        div Cleaning & Staging
        span Our highly-trained, professional cleaners all have 2+ years of experience and do amazing work.
      li
        =image_tag 'icon_linens.png'
        div Linens & Towels
        span High quality luxury linens and towels, commercially pressed and delivered to your property.
      li
        =image_tag 'icon_restocking.png'
        div Restocking Supplies
        span We've partnered with C.O. Bigelow to provide your guests with super high quality toiletries.
